Gary L. West's Biography




			Gary L. West (age 60) Director since 1987 Mr. West co-founded WATS Marketing of America in 1978 and remained
with that company until 1985. He joined West in July 1987 and has served as our Chairman since that time. Gary West and Mary West are husband and
wife. His term will expire in 2008.
		
Source: West Corporation on 04/17/2006
		
	

 
 






