 Detailed Description
			           	           
						One each of four different jerky flavors. Ships in a "Jerky Society" gift box. 

Choose 4oz or 8oz sizes from Original recipe or Certified Angus Beef jerky. 

CAB Steak strips are a little sweeter, a little smokier, and a touch more savory than our original recipe.









